---
title: One-Pan Cheesy Chicken Tacos with Black Beans, Green Pepper & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: We love making tacos at home so we can customize them to fit our exact craving. For this vegetarian version, we ditched the meat for a hearty filling of green pepper and spiced black beans, and two cheeses for maximum melt-factor, plus a drizzle of smoky red pepper crema. Oh, and did we mention these are ready in just 15 minutes?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/661d64d63d20ae432f30b528-0e7d7a3b.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/664e2464b738d70eba6c48f1-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 1010 kcal
  fat: 41 g
  saturated fat: 17 g
  carbohydrates: 85 g
  sugar: 11 g
  protein: 62 g
  fiber: 11 g
